# Project Overview

## Co to za repo

`roduq-design-generator-studio` = **AI-driven design generator** dla Roduq agency.

Fork [nexu-io/open-design](https://github.com/nexu-io/open-design) (Apache-2.0, Next.js 16 + SQLite + Anthropic skills) z Roduq customizations.

## End-state

User wpisuje brief → AI generuje 3 design variants równolegle → user wybiera + eksportuje → `@roduq/cli` (w sister repo `roduq-web-starter`) konsumuje i scaffolduje working website.

**Czas**: brief → AI-designed website w **<5 min** (vs. 2-5 dni manual setup).

## Stack (post-Phase-1, upstream nexu-io/open-design@v0.8.0 merged)

**Monorepo** — pnpm@10.33.2 + node ~24 + TypeScript 5.9.3. Workspace: `apps/*` + `packages/*` + `tools/*` + `e2e`.

**Apps**:
- `apps/web` — Next.js 16 App Router + React 18 (UI runtime, Turbopack dev)
- `apps/daemon` — local privileged daemon + `od` CLI bin + `/api/*` + skills + design systems + artifacts + static serving
- `apps/desktop` — Electron shell (discovers web URL via sidecar IPC)
- `apps/packaged` — thin packaged Electron runtime entry
- `apps/landing-page` — Astro 6 marketing site
- `apps/telemetry-worker` — separate worker process

**Packages** (`packages/*`): contracts (pure TS web/daemon DTOs) / host / platform (OS process primitives) / sidecar / sidecar-proto / plugin-runtime / registry-protocol / agui-adapter / diagnostics / download.

**Content directories**: `skills/` (functional skills) + `design-systems/` (brand DESIGN.md files) + `design-templates/` (rendering catalogue) + `craft/` (universal craft rules) + `prompt-templates/` + `templates/`.

**Local persistence**: Better-sqlite3 (SQLite) — `.od/app.sqlite` (gitignored) z project metadata + per-project artifacts.

**Roduq additions** (per LICENSE-ROduQ.txt):
- `skills/roduq-*` — 7 custom Anthropic skills
- `design-systems/*` — 7 Roduq brand-agnostic presets (default, monolith-meadow, tech-modern, warm-editorial, brutalist, soft-pastel, dark-cinematic)
- `skills/multi-variant` — 3 designs parallel generator
- `src/output/`, `schemas/` — JSON Schema v1 file protocol
- `src/mcp-server.ts` — Claude Code MCP bridge

**Dev lifecycle**: `pnpm tools-dev` (NIE `pnpm dev` — patrz rule 005-coding-standards + AGENTS.md § "Local lifecycle"). Ports via `--daemon-port` / `--web-port` flags, exported jako `OD_PORT` / `OD_WEB_PORT`.

**Windows native = best-effort** per upstream AGENTS.md. Wymaga VS Build Tools 2022+ dla `better-sqlite3` compile (~2min). `corepack enable` fails (EPERM) — use `npm install -g pnpm@10.33.2` directly.

**LLM providers** (abstraction layer Roduq — patrz rule 007): Anthropic Claude Sonnet 4.6+ (primary) / OpenAI GPT-5 (alternative) / Google Gemini 2.5 Pro (alternative) / Mock (CI/dev).

## Sister repo

[`roduq-web-starter`](../roduq-web-starter/) — main monorepo z Astro 6 + Payload CMS + 29 business modules.

**NIE łączymy kodem** — kontrakt to **file protocol** `~/.roduq/output/{client-id}/` (JSON Schema v1 validated). Patrz `.cursor/rules/004-file-protocol.mdc`.

